    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained driver. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia that are typical of highway driving. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats show minimal bolstering wear and no cracks, while the carpets have been protected by all-weather mats since day one. All electronic components, including the heated seats, navigation system, and premium audio, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly with no leaks or unusual noises, backed by a complete service history showing oil changes every 5,000 miles. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. This car has been garage-kept and smoke-free, offering a premium feel and mechanical peace of mind for its next owner.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
